name: Non Internal Dependencies
query:
match (a:NODE_LABEL {`source info`: "SOURCE INFO"})<-[r:flows_into*]-(b:NODE_LABEL)
match (a1:NODE_LABEL_NonInternal)<-[r2:flows_into*]-(b1:NODE_LABEL_NonInternal)
WHERE a.`source info`=a1.`source info`
AND   b.`source info`=b1.`source info`
return a1, r2, b1

name: Explicit Dependencies
query:
match (a:NODE_LABEL {`source info`: "SOURCE INFO"})<-[r:flows_into*]-(b:NODE_LABEL)
match (a1:NODE_LABEL_Explicit)<-[r2:flows_into*]-(b1:NODE_LABEL_Explicit)
WHERE a.`source info`=a1.`source info`
AND   b.`source info`=b1.`source info`
return a1, r2, b1

name: Non Internal Dependents
query:
match (a:NODE_LABEL {`source info`: "SOURCE INFO"})-[r:flows_into*]->(b:NODE_LABEL)
match (a1:NODE_LABEL_NonInternal)-[r2:flows_into*]->(b1:NODE_LABEL_NonInternal)
WHERE a.`source info`=a1.`source info`
AND   b.`source info`=b1.`source info`
return a1, r2, b1

query:
